PN,41801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784877490
OL,3,CCalls for ring-fenced funding for NI
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,FA south Belfast business owner has
OL,7,Fcalled for any funding from the new
OL,8,FPrime Minister to help the high
OL,9,Fstreet, to be ring-fenced in Northern
OL,10,FIreland, so that it must be spent
OL,11,Fhelping businesses.
OL,13,FChris O'Reilly recently had to close a
OL,14,Fshop on the Ormeau Road.
OL,16,FHe told UTV that increases to national
OL,17,Finsurance costs were "the final nail
OL,18,Fin the coffin" that resulted in the
OL,19,Fshutters being pulled down on his
OL,20,Fconvenience store.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784877490
OL,3,CCalls for ring-fenced funding for NI
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,FAndy Burnham is being urged to change
OL,7,Fdirection or risk the closure of more
OL,8,Fbusinesses across the UK.
OL,10,FMr O'Reilly's business closed on the
OL,11,F29th March this year, at the beginning
OL,12,Fof the new financial year.
OL,14,FSome staff were moved elsewhere while
OL,15,Fothers were let go completely.
OL,17,FHe said the store was "no longer
OL,18,Ffinancially viable".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784877490
OL,3,CCalls for ring-fenced funding for NI
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,F"Costs had got really, really out of
OL,7,Fcontrol, from costs that we couldn't
OL,8,Freally control ourselves, and we had
OL,9,Fto make the difficult decision to pull
OL,10,Fthe shutters down.
OL,12,F"The thing that really sort of put us
OL,13,Funder pressure at the very end was the
OL,14,Fdecision to increase the National
OL,15,FInsurance, which has had a cumulative
OL,16,Feffect over the basically the two
OL,17,Fyears that it's been in place now,"
OL,18,FChris added.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784877490
OL,3,CCalls for ring-fenced funding for NI
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,F"It's nearly tripled, so it was it's
OL,7,Fclose to #100,000 in a trading year.
OL,8,FAnd for a convenience store business
OL,9,Fthat operate on on on very, very tight
OL,10,Fmargins, it was just too much for us."
OL,12,FPolicies announced by Downing Street
OL,13,Fcan allow money to come to Northern
OL,14,FIreland, but it doesn't necessarily
OL,15,Falways go to the same type of scheme.
OL,17,FChris said that ring-fencing money
OL,18,F"absolutely has to happen" to provide
OL,19,Fhelp for a small business like his.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784877490
OL,3,CCalls for ring-fenced funding for NI
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,F"We've we've seen where independent
OL,7,Fretail did not get supported through
OL,8,Fthe rate relief scheme. From a small
OL,9,Fbusiness operation point of view,
OL,10,Fcoming out of COVID, we've seen
OL,11,Findependent retailers across the water
OL,12,Fget supported with rate reduction
OL,13,Fschemes," he said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784877490
OL,3,CCalls for ring-fenced funding for NI
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,F"And the money was coming across here
OL,7,Fin principle, and there was a
OL,8,Fministerial decision to put that put
OL,9,Fthat elsewhere. And as a result of
OL,10,Fthat, that was one of the nails in the
OL,11,Fcoffin that that that brought the end
OL,12,Fof the brought the end of this
OL,13,Fbusiness."
OL,15,FAndy Burnham made another policy
OL,16,Fannouncement as part of his quest to
OL,17,Ftackle the cost-of-living crisis.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
