OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784877490
OL,3,CCalls for ring-fenced funding for NI
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, a decision to cut VAT on
OL,7,Felectricity bills was made, but on
OL,8,FWednesday morning it was announced bus
OL,9,Ffares will be capped at #2 in England
OL,10,Ffrom January.
OL,12,FThe nationwide cap is currently set at
OL,13,F#3 until the end of March 2027
OL,14,Falthough some areas ` including London
OL,15,Fand Greater Manchester, where Mr
OL,16,FBurnham set a #2 limit as mayor ` have
OL,17,Flower top rates for single tickets.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784877490
OL,3,CCalls for ring-fenced funding for NI
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,FMr Burnham said: "This is about
OL,7,Freprioritising in this phase. As I
OL,8,Fsay, going to the public's priorities:
OL,9,Fthe cost-of-living crisis, the housing
OL,10,Fcrisis. How much longer are we going
OL,11,Fto talk about these things without
OL,12,Factually doing something to help
OL,13,Fpeople?
OL,15,F"And already in the space of a few
OL,16,Fdays, I've made a number of moves that
OL,17,Fwill deal with some of these
OL,18,Fchallenges, although I appreciate
OL,19,Fthere's a lot more to do."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784877490
OL,3,CCalls for ring-fenced funding for NI
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,FThe First and Deputy First Ministers
OL,7,Fheld their first call with the new
OL,8,FSecretary of State.
OL,10,FThe Executive Office said the pair
OL,11,Fspoke about a range of issues with Sir
OL,12,FChris Bryant.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, the Taoiseach, Micheal
OL,15,FMartin, spoke with Andy Burnham on
OL,16,FTuesday night.
OL,18,FMr Martin said: "We had a very warm
OL,19,Fconversation, Secretary Burnham and I.
OL,20,FWe discussed a wide range of issues.
OL,21,FWe look forward to an early meeting.
OL,26,@vD@`rp
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784877490
OL,3,CCalls for ring-fenced funding for NI
OL,4,Cbusinesses
OL,6,F"In terms of Northern Ireland legacy,
OL,7,Fwe did discuss that, which is
OL,8,Fimportant that we bring that to a
OL,9,Fconclusion. I think it's a historic
OL,10,Fopportunity to get legacy done. And we
OL,11,Fand I made those points to Andy."
OL,13,FAny money flowing from Westminster to
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland due to the Prime
OL,15,FMinister's new policies won't likely
OL,16,Fbe clear until the autumn budget.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
